<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>From J to I - The Journey with You</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
                #FFD700 0%, 
                #FFA500 25%, 
                #FF6347 50%, 
                #FF1493 75%, 
                #8A2BE2 100%);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientShift 8s ease infinite;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-shadow: 
                0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8),
                0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.6),
                0 0 30px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            animation: titleGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes titleGlow {
            from {
                text-shadow: 
                    0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8),
                    0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.6),
                    0 0 30px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.4);
            }
            to {
                text-shadow: 
                    0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 1),
                    0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8),
                    0 0 40px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.6);
            }
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .letter-display {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .letter-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 300px;
            height: 400px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, 
                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%,
                rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2) 50%,
                rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.1) 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 
                0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
                inset 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .profile-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 20px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(2deg); }
        }

        .letter-i {
            font-size: 12rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-shadow: 
                0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 1),
                0 0 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8),
                0 0 60px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.6),
                0 0 80px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.4);
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            animation: letterPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes letterPulse {
            from {
                text-shadow: 
                    0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 1),
                    0 0 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8),
                    0 0 60px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.6),
                    0 0 80px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.4);
            }
            to {
                text-shadow: 
                    0 0 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 1),
                    0 0 50px rgba(255, 215, 0, 1),
                    0 0 70px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.8),
                    0 0 90px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.6);
            }
        }

        .text-content {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 0%,
                rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1) 50%,
                rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.05) 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 
                0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2),
                inset 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Large background letter I - similar to J in second code */
        .text-content::before {
            content: 'I';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffd700, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4, #45b7d1);
            background-size: 300% 300%;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            color: transparent;
            opacity: 0.25;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: gradientShiftI 4s ease-in-out infinite, letterFloatI 8s ease-in-out infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.5)) 
                    drop-shadow(0 0 50px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.4))
                    drop-shadow(0 0 70px rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.3));
        }

        @keyframes gradientShiftI {
            0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        }

        @keyframes letterFloatI {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
            25% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(1deg) scale(1.02); }
            50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-1deg) scale(0.98); }
            75% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0.5deg) scale(1.01); }
        }

        .text-content::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, 
                transparent 40%,
                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 50%,
                transparent 60%);
            animation: shimmer 4s ease-in-out infinite;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%) rotate(45deg); }
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .description strong {
            color: #FFD700;
            text-shadow: 
                0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8),
                0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .inner-light-i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #FFD700;
            text-shadow: 
                0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 1),
                0 0 20px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.8),
                0 0 30px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.4);
            animation: innerGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 5px;
        }

        @keyframes innerGlow {
            from {
                text-shadow: 
                    0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 1),
                    0 0 20px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.8),
                    0 0 30px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.4);
            }
            to {
                text-shadow: 
                    0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 1),
                    0 0 30px rgba(255, 165, 0, 1),
                    0 0 40px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.6);
            }
        }

        .floating-lights {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .light-particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: floatUp 8s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes floatUp {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(100vh) scale(0);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            10% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            90% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-100px) scale(1);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            
            .main-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .letter-container {
                width: 250px;
                height: 300px;
            }
            
            .letter-i {
                font-size: 8rem;
            }
            
            .text-content {
                padding: 30px;
            }
            
            .text-content::before {
                font-size: 18rem;
            }
            
            .description {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .text-content::before {
                font-size: 14rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="floating-lights"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="main-title">I-infinite you</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="letter-display">
                 <div class="letter-container">
            <!-- ✅ Image only -->
            <img src="/asset/cube21.jpg" alt="Jyoti" class="profile-image">
        </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-content">
                <div class="description">
                    <!-- The journey from <strong>J</strong> to <span class="inner-light-i">i</span> – more than letters, it's <strong>hope</strong>, <strong>strength</strong>, and <strong>love</strong>...  -->
                    <!-- <br><br> -->
                    For me <span class="inner-light-i">JYOTI</span> isn't just a name – it's the emotion that keep me going through tough days, the smile that made me believe in love exist...
                    <br><br>
                    <strong>Jyoti</strong>, you are my <strong>direction</strong>, my <strong>purpose</strong>, my <strong>inner light</strong> and<span class="inner-light-i">forever my babygirl</span>
                    <br><br>
                    The journey just started and  <strong>continue </strong>with my <strong>strong girl..</strong>.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Create floating light particles
        function createFloatingLights() {
            const container = document.querySelector('.floating-lights');
            
            for (let i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
                const light = document.createElement('div');
                light.className = 'light-particle';
                light.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
                light.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 8 + 's';
                light.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 5) + 's';
                container.appendChild(light);
            }
        }

        // Initialize floating lights
        createFloatingLights();

        // Add more particles periodically
        setInterval(createFloatingLights, 8000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>